ActAppropriation Act No. 1, 2011-12
PrecisAppointment of SYLVIA CESARATTO as Ambassador Extraordinary and Plenipotentiary of Canada to the Republic of Panama; DAVID CHATTERSON as Ambassador Extraordinary and Plenipotentiary of Canada to the Republic of Korea with concurrent accreditation to the Democratic People’s Republic of Korea; GENEVIÈVE DES RIVIÈRES as Ambassador Extraordinary and Plenipotentiary of Canada to the People’s Democratic Republic of Algeria; DAVID DEVINE as High Commissioner for Canada to the Co-operative Republic of Guyana; DOUGLAS GEORGE as Ambassador Extraordinary and Plenipotentiary of Canada to the State of Kuwait; HEIDI KUTZ as Ambassador Extraordinary and Plenipotentiary of Canada to the Portuguese Republic; TROY LULASHNYK as Ambassador Extraordinary and Plenipotentiary of Canada to the Ukraine; TIMOTHY MARTIN as Ambassador Extraordinary and Plenipotentiary of Canada to the Republic of Colombia; ROBERT PECK as Ambassador Extraordinary and Plenipotentiary of Canada to the Hellenic Republic and as High Commissioner for Canada to the Republic of Cyprus; DAVID PLUNKETT as Ambassador Extraordinary and Plenipotentiary of Canada to the European Union; and HUGHES ROUSSEAU as Ambassador Extraordinary and Plenipotentiary of Canada to the Republic of Guatemala and as High Commissioner for Canada to Belize.
